    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract listener for game state transition events. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Implementations can react to state exits, entries, and transitions. Listeners are notified by the <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1gamestate_1_1GameStateManager" kindref="compound">GameStateManager</ref> when state changes occur.</para>
